Function Requirement:
User registration (player and manager)
Profile management (player and manager)
Recording and updating player performance statistics.
Logging individual training sessions.
Scheduling training sessions and tournaments.
Medical records history for players.
Attendance tracking for training sessions and tournaments
Player physical record.
Facility record.
Tournament registration.
Player allowance management.
Accommodation player and manager.
Player ledger record.
Medical appointment booking.
Players and managers apply and record leave.
Warning notification platform for player and manager.

Non-Function Requirement:
System availability 99.9%.
Encryption and authorized access only.
Intuitive UI design for coaches and players.
Ability to handle growth in player registration.
Rapid page load times (under 2 seconds).
Regular database backups for record recovery.
Support for users with diverse needs.
Accuracy and consistency of tournament and performance data.

